continuous monitoring --> why?

1. Server Health --> uptime, CPU, Memory, Disk
2. Performance --> Response time, Status code, Errors
3. Troubleshoot applications
4. Alerts


Role of DevOps / SRE Engineer -->

1. Proof of concept (POC)
2. Setup/install monitoring tool
3. Create Dashboards for metrics --> uptime, CPU, Memory, Disk, Response time, Status code, Errors,..
4. setup Alerts and acting on alerts and SOPs (Standard Operating Procedures)

--> Prometheus & Grafana

General Architecture of Monitoring tool -->

* Database to store metrics
* Agents on the datasources
* Visualization tool

Prometheus --> DB
Grafana --> Visualization tool
Exporters ---> agent 

Prometheus --> time-series DB
influxDB


https://prometheus.io/docs/introduction/overview/
https://prometheus.io/docs/instrumenting/clientlibs/
https://prometheus.io/docs/instrumenting/exporters/

